quran[32{c,v,t}:
86,1,Wassamaaa'i wattaariq
86,2,Wa maaa adraaka mattaariq
86,3,Annajmus saaqib
86,4,In kullu nafsil lammaa 'alaihaa haafiz
86,5,Fal yanzuril insaanu mimma khuliq
86,6,Khuliqa mim maaa'in daafiq
86,7,Yakhruju mim bainissulbi wat taraaa'ib
86,8,Innahoo 'alaa raj'ihee laqaadir
86,9,Yawma tublas saraaa'ir
86,10,Famaa lahoo min quwwatinw wa laa naasir
86,11,Wassamaaa'i zaatir raj'
86,12,Wal ardi zaatis sad'
86,13,Innahoo laqawlun fasl
86,14,Wa maa huwa bil hazl
86,15,Innahum yakeedoona kaidaa
86,16,Wa akeedu kaidaa
86,17,Famahhilil kaafireena amhilhum ruwaidaa
87,1,Sabbihisma Rabbikal A'laa
87,2,Allazee khalaqa fasawwaa
87,3,Wallazee qaddara fahadaa
87,4,Wallazeee akhrajal mar'aa
87,5,Faja'alahoo ghusaaa'an ahwaa
87,6,Sanuqri'uka falaa tansaaa
87,7,Illaa maa shaaa'al laah; innahoo ya'lamul jahra wa maa yakhfaa
87,8,Wa nu-yassiruka lilyusraa
87,9,Fazakkir in nafa'atizzikraa
87,10,Sa yazzakkaru maiyakhshaa
87,11,Wa yatajannabuhal ashqaa
87,12,Allazee yaslan Naaral kubraa
87,13,Summa laa yamootu feehaa wa laa yahyaa
87,14,Qad aflaha man tazakkaa
87,15,Wa zakaras ma Rabbihee fasallaa
